{"tid":641252,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"258湯臣集團.高息?","createTime":"2018-04-25T01:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T17:53:14.000Z","uid":291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a497986c1d3c559117f3faac62c7e4f84ddf29f1","tid":641252,"uid":291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"258湯臣集團.叫唔叫高息??<br />\n黎緊有43仙息,又講到純利有12.55億...........<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有入呢隻野?"},{"pid":"f54941ae6b143bdd960ec23dd3c1c0a405bb5e16","tid":641252,"uid":22614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"From aastocks<br />\n<br />\n(06-Mar) 湯臣集團(<a href=\"http://00258.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00258.HK&d=b08jASaIXUQ8mQAcfbnz6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=08216f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00258.HK</a>)  0.000 (0.000%)   發盈喜，雖然去年經營收益總額有所下降，但料純利較2016年之8.76億元，大幅增長約40%，主要因為去年1月完成出售天津津灣置業51%股權，另外在去年8月完成出售天津湯臣建設100%股權而確認收益所致。<br />\n<br />\n(27-Mar) 湯臣集團(<a href=\"http://00258.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00258.HK&d=b08jASaIXUQ8mQAcfbnz6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=08216f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00258.HK</a>)  0.000 (0.000%)   公布2017年止年度業績，收入21.07億元，按年下降48.7%。錄得純利12.55億元，增長43.3%，每股盈利69.44仙。中期息維持43仙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇盤數好似mama, 雖則息好似唔錯"},{"pid":"e88100219bf8fefefbe1d069f6e226f383616e80","tid":641252,"uid":291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:06:04.000Z","msg":"好似無咩人留意咁...就黎除靜"},{"pid":"8a15331a02c67c57ad860ec9fbd61baac85014db","tid":641252,"uid":291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"湯臣集團 (<a href=\"http://00258.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00258.HK&d=b08jASaIXUQ8mQAcfbnz6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=08216f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00258.HK</a>)  建議增加10億股法定股本<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00258/NOW.869852/all